{"tid":2262011,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚龜撚] 新手求救","createTime":"2020-10-28T18:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T19:49:42.000Z","uid":75190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0692183b74365988e785096bf7d579652067c0f","tid":2262011,"uid":75190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T18:15:54.000Z","msg":"最近接左隻斑龜返屋企養<br />\n呢幾日發現佢個殼有一層白色衣<br />\n上水唔明顯，水入面睇就好似有層白色毛毛/ 膜咁<br />\n上網睇左好多資料，<br />\n都唔肯定佢係生水霉定係正常脫皮<br />\n請大家幫手睇下張圖指點下😫<br />\n<br />\n觀察左佢幾日，<br />\n發現佢唔太鍾意上陸地，<br />\n但都會間中游水幾活潑咁<br />\n一日兩餐，食完即柯<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/10/29/pXnkBJ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F10%2F29%2FpXnkBJ.jpeg&h=8af302d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/10/29/5wfnKS.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F10%2F29%2F5wfnKS.jpeg&h=50ca00d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c16b47bd22f7b4500f8633fe98f677e9e3a4635d","tid":2262011,"uid":75190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff6adf4c39412c657f15f5be7ad89f7d3e458c0","tid":2262011,"uid":75190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T18:17:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27ecf87ac61e5908a1929c5536ccf97d8f6b258","tid":2262011,"uid":75190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T18:18:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957020a8325753c91bdd805f4b75663663666d55","tid":2262011,"u